<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/29813296">如果你是三国志里的许攸，会怎样利用官渡之战的功绩呢？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4108072" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">好奇，想知道如果你跟原来那个喜欢吹嘘的许攸比较，你会怎样利用这次的功绩呢！ </div>


</div>
